  "title": "Laundry Driver Class 4",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<p><br>\n• Collect soiled laundry from customers and deliver clean laundry to Hotel, Restaurant or commercial locations on time.<br>\n• Plan and follow an efficient delivery route to maximize time and fuel usage while meeting customer deadlines.<br>\n• Provide friendly and professional customer service when picking up or delivering laundry, addressing any questions or concerns.<br>\n• Maintain accurate records of deliveries and pickups, including customer information, special instructions, and completed tasks.<br>\n• Regularly inspect the delivery vehicle, ensuring it is clean, fueled, and well-maintained. Report any mechanical issues or required repairs to supervisors.<br>\n• Strong customer service and communication skills.<br>\n• Basic organizational skills for handling orders, paperwork, and delivery schedules.<br>\n• Ability to work independently and manage time effectively.<br>\n• Valid driver’s license and a clean driving record.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min 'N' or 'O' Level.</li>\n  <li>Valid Class 4 Driving License.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 1-year driving experience.</li>\n  <li>Proficient in English.</li>\n  <li>Bilingual is an advantage.</li>\n  <li>Able to Work on Weekends.</li>\n  <li>Ensure timely collection and delivery of client's items.</li>\n  <li>Be part of a dynamic and fast-growing business with training and guidance provided.</li>\n  <li>Team Player.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Singaporean, SPR are welcome.</p>",
